        "gg1-nBNIy9D_text": "<p>\"For weeks, my lower back pain was so intense I couldn’t get through a meal without shifting around in my seat. I’ve tried everything - heat creams, stretching, even prescription meds. Nothing really helped. <strong>Honestly, I didn’t expect much from a patch…</strong> but after the very first one, I sat pain-free for the rest of the evening. Total game-changer. I'm never going without these again.\"</p>",
        "ggV2Gzg1kTE_text": "<p>Lisa M.</p>",
        "gg3ero32Veq_text": "<p>Verified Purchase</p>",
        "ggc8Jx1axa0_text": "<p>Name</p>",
