        "ggMqSUhQV7T_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-43b4ab28-517e-42b7-8b4a-a042d7cd05b2.jpg",
        "ggDMIiaV6W6_text": "<p>\"For weeks, my lower back pain was so intense I couldn’t get through a meal without shifting around in my seat. I’ve tried everything - heat creams, stretching, even prescription meds. Nothing really helped. <strong>Honestly,</strong> <strong>I didn’t expect much from a patch…</strong> but after the very first one, I sat pain-free for the rest of the evening. Total game-changer. I'm never going without these again.\"</p>",
