    "gp_section_589747403201446677": {
      "type": "gp-section-589747403201446677",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "ddebae74ade4ff5d02a9f71967341e43d913233969fa5b5acbd480c31e6d133b_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggGkzemG1js_text": "<span style=\"color:#055BDC;\"><strong>No more wincing, limping, or bracing for pain - just clean, natural relief that lasts.</strong></span>",
        "ggWQIG9fsLw_text": "The Real Problem Isn’t Just the Pain - It’s What It’s Taking From You ",
        "ggpMggARnnc_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8e88438a-965e-49bd-a32b-a51a7e9ea16a.png",
        "ggymlr3ksYA_text": "The Real Problem Isn’t Just the Pain - It’s What It’s Taking From You ",
        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>Back, hip, knee pain and sciatica don’t just hurt - <strong>they wear you down.</strong> They steal your sleep, slow you down, and make everyday tasks feel impossible.</p>",
        "gg4YoJ0BCta_text": "<p>And most people just push through. They settle. But <strong>the longer you live with pain, the more it chips away</strong> at your energy, movement, and quality of life.</p>",
        "ggQAm8x-ujQ_text": "<p>You don’t need a band-aid. You need <strong>real support</strong> that helps your body heal - not just cope.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_589747403201118997": {
      "type": "gp-section-589747403201118997",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "0d664595df43818bd5c28834668e7bcecfd64dd87f12eb5a01ce9ffe43b368a7_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggzRfc3KmKh_text": "Here’s How Real Relief Actually Works",
        "ggqH4FcsZET_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f7ba0a07-21f3-443d-b851-a33b796d1637.png",
        "ggclZmxOds__text": "Here’s How Real Relief Actually Works",
        "gg5gEyQLqLG_text": "<p>To stop the cycle of pain, you need to go deeper - <strong>not just numb it.</strong> That means increasing blood flow, reducing inflammation, and quieting the nerves that keep firing pain signals.</p>",
        "ggxA_OF-tV-_text": "<p><strong>That’s exactly what these patches do.</strong> Each one delivers a powerful blend of natural herbs and soothing heat directly where you need it - helping your body <strong>calm inflammation, restore circulation, and start healing from within.</strong></p>",
        "gg-RifOCijk_text": "<p>It’s not a mask for the pain. It’s a reset button for the areas that need it most.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_589747403201250069": {
      "type": "gp-section-589747403201250069",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "3e6ee77ea87c83671c0d0178527c415302f264f367c8641921b26b21d51799f1_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg7Yy94Ir4K_text": "Powered by Potent, Natural Ingredients",
        "ggXilITdP9U_text": "<p>Each patch is infused with a time-tested blend of traditional herbs and warming agents designed to calm inflammation, boost circulation, and relieve pain fast.</p>",
        "ggQ-YblN67C_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b6309e9b-be77-4e24-af56-f1c76618d9f3.jpg",
        "ggqmXaR2G49_text": "<p>Aconite Root </p>",
        "gghbQ3brrGX_text": "<p>A powerful warming herb used in Traditional Chinese Medicine to improve blood flow and relieve deep joint, muscle, and nerve pain.</p>",
        "gg-XPu10T26_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-911790b8-d4b4-4162-9107-b48f7683b53c.jpg",
        "gg_z6c4B0nZ_text": "<p>Chili (Capsicum) </p>",
        "ggBfCGU_793_text": "<p>Famous for its deep heat — this natural compound helps block pain signals and reduce inflammation with a fast-acting warming effect.</p>",
        "ggFZaaL3BVN_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-e44f0571-dc3a-4a9f-9371-cff7111aedf6.jpg",
        "ggDd67YTL_5_text": "<p>Menthol</p>",
        "gg2x1ZQzmie_text": "<p>Cools on contact while stimulating circulation, helping to relax stiff joints and muscles and calm down nerve irritation.</p>",
        "ggQHGWW7Eeu_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-a931bde0-0389-40ae-92c0-5641ab5bd814.png",
        "ggWZ3sCnORx_text": "<p>Dried Ginger</p>",
        "ggFFHFli7b-_text": "<p>A natural anti-inflammatory and antioxidant that supports the body’s healing process while easing pain and swelling.</p>",
        "ggxmYAj796X_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-a63cd5b4-fb1a-4d73-b921-8ab70eb6115e.jpg",
        "gg0tZCOehfD_text": "<p>Artemisia argyi leaf</p>",
        "ggwB-q6UFbl_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-ba8112c3-6e95-4480-9f2e-a4e8cd1f1590.jpg",
        "ggpBHM4ze1P_text": "<p>Camphor</p>",
        "ggAHCpm0eIP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-0d48d21b-b5e9-4ce1-82e6-3e52ceb5d904.jpg",
        "ggGfA6Kh_pm_text": "<p>Kusnetzoff monkshood root</p>",
        "ggUfM-_1YAo_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8bc88472-a91b-455f-b5e7-b947843f856e.jpg",
        "ggYTiOSHusp_text": "<p>Borneol</p>"
      }
