    "gp_section_589747403200987925": {
      "type": "gp-section-589747403200987925",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "5592ac3040c8f9189c168b7c2cc724f6283706bf27067a0373642b942eed7ab2_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggBJa8Yn5GB_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_0": "<p>How fast will I feel relief?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_1": "<p>How long does each patch last?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_2": "<p>How do I use the patches?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_3": "<p>Can I use more than one patch at a time?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_4": "<p>Are there any side effects?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_5": "<p>Who are these patches for?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_6": "<p>Do they work for chronic pain?</p>",
        "ggJ59b-ywE__text": "<p>Most users feel noticeable relief within 15–30 minutes of applying the patch. Results may vary depending on the severity of the pain.</p>",
        "ggOF78_pLax_text": "<p>Each patch delivers up to <strong>8–12 hours</strong> of continuous pain relief and support.</p>",
        "ggGBgdMGN1b_text": "<p>Just peel, stick to the painful area (lower back, spine, hips, etc.), and let the patch do the rest. For best results, use consistently.</p>",
        "gg5779-Q2LD_text": "<p>Yes - patches can be used on multiple areas of the body simultaneously if needed. Always follow your skin’s sensitivity.</p>",
        "ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text": "<p>Our patches are made with natural ingredients and are generally well tolerated. If you have very sensitive skin or a known allergy to herbal ingredients, test on a small area first or consult your doctor.</p>",
        "ggGIleTpKvk_text": "<p>They’re ideal for people dealing with <strong>back pain, sciatica, inflammation, stiffness, or general muscle fatigue</strong> - especially side sleepers, older adults, or those with desk jobs or physical labor.</p>",
        "ggiybgH7i8i_text": "<p>Many users with chronic conditions (like sciatica, arthritis, or herniated discs) have found relief. While results vary, consistent use helps reduce flare-ups and improve mobility over time.</p>"
      }
    },
